** Functions inj different Module:-
____________________________________________________

01 PreWorks for going ahead.
02 Function Component in Different Module.
____________________________________________________

01 PreWorks for going ahead:-(Arrange Folder Structure):-
______________________________________________________________
01 If already not created, create a components folder inside the src folder.
02 Then create a folder with any name(E.g:- counter) inside the components folder.
03 Then create a file with any name(counter.jsx) inside counter folder.


02 Function Component in Different Module:-
_______________________________________________________
01 Create a function with any name.(E.g:-Counter)
   E.g:- function Counter()
02 Import React from react.
   E.g:- import React  from "react";
03 In the Buttom of the class do the export default.
   E.g:-export default Counter

** Now comes into the App.js and do some changes here also:-

01 Give the entry for Counter.jsx inside the App.js.
   E.g:-<Counter></Counter>
02 Import the counter from  folder structure.
   E.g:- import Counter  from './components/counter/counter';

   Now,Hit the browser....I hope We are able to see the output.
   
                                       Thanks !   Happy Learning.
